SUMMARY—Requires the establishment and carrying out of a program to
supplement the available food supply for certain persons in
certain circumstances. (BDR 38-1103)
FISCAL NOTE: Effect on Local Government: No.
Effect on the State: Contains Appropriation not included in
Executive Budget.
